    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A Dual Ascent is a <strong>solo-cooperative adventure</strong> game in which you control both characters simultaneously with a single controller. Guide them as they ascend the Mountain, following a story inspired by fairy tales:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >     <i>&quot;Once upon a time, there was a mountain; a mountain so tall, it touched the sky. It was <strong>the Great Mountain of Wonders</strong>.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>      An <strong>Old Pilgrim</strong>, who came from a land far away, was on his way to the summit.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>      But a fallen <strong>Little Star</strong> had the exact same idea, for she thought she might return home, if she reached the top of the Mountain...&quot;</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239640/extras/dc4097586b239da4b4dbfb30ab264dcc.poster.avif?t=1734488891\" width=604 height=340 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239640/extras/dc4097586b239da4b4dbfb30ab264dcc.webm?t=1734488891\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239640/extras/dc4097586b239da4b4dbfb30ab264dcc.mp4?t=1734488891\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This is how the tale of two peculiar characters begins.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Come set out on a <strong>poetic journey</strong> that will <strong>challenge</strong> your mind and ability!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u>Control the Old Pilgrim and the Little Star <strong>at the same time, with one controller</strong></u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239640/extras/bede15a8becadfbec6fb0f6dfeaa5fa2.poster.avif?t=1734488891\" width=604 height=340 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239640/extras/bede15a8becadfbec6fb0f6dfeaa5fa2.webm?t=1734488891\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239640/extras/bede15a8becadfbec6fb0f6dfeaa5fa2.mp4?t=1734488891\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u>Solve <strong>unique and innovative puzzles</strong></u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239640/extras/e257f32b296f3f1a6549f65096038745.poster.avif?t=1734488891\" width=604 height=340 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239640/extras/e257f32b296f3f1a6549f65096038745.webm?t=1734488891\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239640/extras/e257f32b296f3f1a6549f65096038745.mp4?t=1734488891\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u>Discover <strong>wonderful  environments</strong> inspired by fairy tales</u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239640/extras/800eafabb7876eecd0dfa3d4006fcdec.poster.avif?t=1734488891\" width=604 height=340 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239640/extras/800eafabb7876eecd0dfa3d4006fcdec.webm?t=1734488891\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239640/extras/800eafabb7876eecd0dfa3d4006fcdec.mp4?t=1734488891\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>                        Will you solve the riddles of the Great Mountain of Wonders?</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >                             <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239640/extras/e444f0b9e57c3f5a95834094eec309ba.avif?t=1734488891\" width=336 height=626 /></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>NB:</i> A Dual Ascent<i> is a graduation game made in one year by a team of 9 students. <br>Thank you for your consideration regarding potential bugs and performance issues. </i></p>",
